): T ={}> {
    handle! fn {
        DecideOrFail.decide(() => k) => {
            backtrackReverse<T>(() => k(false), () => backtrackReverse<T>(() => k(true), orElse))
        },
        DecideOrFail.fail(() => _) => {
            orElse()
        },
        pure(x) => x
    }
}

